data.description: FIRST TIME ON THE MARKET CUSTOM BUILT BY ORIGINAL OWNERS! Don't miss this all-brick split level sitting on a double lot. The main level offers 3 generously sized bedrooms, including the owner's suite with double closets and private bath with jacuzzi and wheelchair accessible shower and adjacent four seasons room. Formal living and dining rooms make hosting family and friends a breeze. The family room is the perfect place to relax, anchored by a timeless and cozy brick fireplace. The full finished basement with full bath offers great storage and fantastic entertaining space with a huge rec room, wet bar and full bathroom. The fenced in double lot is perfect for kids play, pets or family cookouts. Convenient access to expressway, public transportation, schools, shopping and entertainment.  Home is being sold AS-IS.
